OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with further
OL,6,Foutbreaks of mostly light drizzle over
OL,7,Fthe hills, and limited brighter
OL,8,Fbreaks. Wetter into the afternoon with
OL,9,Fa more organised band of rain sinking
OL,10,Fsouthwards, clearing most by the
OL,11,Fevening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBand of rain clearing
OL,14,Fsouthwards this evening, followed by
OL,15,Foccasional clear periods and a few
OL,16,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
