OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA chilly start to the day
OL,6,Fbut mostly dry with sunny spells.
OL,7,FSunshine turning hazy into the
OL,8,Fafternoon with rain arriving later in
OL,9,Fthe evening. Feeling cooler.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FTurning
OL,12,Funsettled over the Easter weekend with
OL,13,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,14,FBrighter spells expected mainly on
OL,15,FSunday. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,16,Ftoo.
